- intercept bursts of input

- keep marks when F5 refreshing

- introduce SIGQUIT for interrupt multi?

- add -o commandline option for starting with a certain sort mode

- re-introduce (M)ore-(A)cl command.
  aclget()
  acledit()
  aclput()

